{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Welcome to Mr. Pompy's Extravagant Quiz! The only quiz to outbeat your brain!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Welcome to the Extravagant Quiz!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mr. Pompy's Extravagant Quiz is a psychological horror experience in an old edutainment quiz game. In this game, you are tasked with helping Mr. Pompy and his friends, Patrick and PomPom, find and collect golden items. The only way to get these golden items is through quizzes. Collecting them all will then prove you to be an extravagant genius!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">How It Started</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Congratulations! You're one of the few people who has received our unique cereal box copies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i>*NOTE: Any future giveaways of this game are to be discontinued indefinitely. Any customers to get their hands on a copy are a lost cause.</i></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998260/extras/case_send_2.gif?t=1738003654\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Meet the Crew! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>You've got PomPom!</strong> Her lively and boisterous personality can help you solve math problems and, all in all, lift your mood. Visit her store occasionally to purchase her several treats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998260/extras/pompom_card.png?t=1738003654\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Next is Patrick!</strong> He will speed you through all you need to know about history and science. Perhaps even to the extent where you greatly surpass him. Visit his library whenever you have some free time to learn about interesting topics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998260/extras/patrick_card.png?t=1738003654\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Finally, we have Mr. Pompy himself!</strong> As your host, he will ensure that you win the game with nothing less than  perfection and a more positive attitude towards life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998260/extras/pompy_card.gif?t=1738003654\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Puzzles &amp; Quizzes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do puzzles to proceed to the quiz: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998260/extras/game_prev_3.gif?t=1738003654\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Test your smarts with our amazing quizzes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998260/extras/game_prev_4.gif?t=1738003654\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">See how well you did:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998260/extras/game_prev_5.gif?t=1738003654\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Brought to you by Light Thoughts Game Company. Discover the light within your mind.</h2>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998260/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738003654","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998260/page.bg.jpg?t=1738003654","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998260/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738003654","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2998260/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738003654","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Welcome to Mr. Pompy's Extravagant Quiz! The only quiz to outbeat y